msgid "**Questions**"
msgstr ""

msgid "What's happening in the cloud when I run a server?"
msgstr ""

msgid "How many CPU cores and RAM do I need?"
msgstr ""

msgid "How can I reinstate the default environment of a user's server?"
msgstr ""

