msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Users can launch servers with a variety of resources available, namely "
"the number of CPU cores and RAM."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"It is important to use cloud resources responsibly to maximize efficiency"
" and minimize carbon emissions."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Hub Champions can stop, restart and gain control of a user's server for "
"troubleshooting purposes."
